  "title": "Sales & Project Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<p>- Develop monthly, quarterly, and annual sales plans;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Develop and implement strategies to bring in new business;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Pursue new sales opportunities, gather inbound leads, and follow-up calls/meetings;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Work effectively with internal stakeholders &amp; external vendor to achieve business goals;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To understand the material costing for printing, carpentery and signages;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To understand the operation of printers, summa cutter, CCD CNC &amp; Oscillating machine and CCD Laser cutter;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To understand the labour cost for production;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To attend briefing/meeting and site measurements for production for the projects undertaking;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To ensure the production of the projects undertaking;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To ensure the installation and delivery of the projects undertaking.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements :</strong></p>\n<p>- Diploma or Degree in any field;</p>\n<p>- At least 2 or 3 years of corporate sales experience/ project management;<br>\n- Proficient in MS Office (Excel, Word, PowerPoint);<br>\n- Strong time management skills;<br>\n- Passion for relationship building and selling;<br>\n- Strong presentation and negotiation skills;<br>\n- Customer service- orientated attitude;<br>\n- Ambitious and driven personality with a hunger for success.</p>",
